@CreoleResource(name="Jape Viewer",
                comment="A JAPE grammar file viewer",
                helpURL="http://gate.ac.uk/userguide/chap:jape",
                guiType=LARGE,
                mainViewer=true,
                resourceDisplayed="gate.creole.Transducer")
public class JapeViewer
extends AbstractVisualResource
implements ANNIEConstants, ProgressListener

A JAPE viewer that allows access to all phases of the grammar and provides syntax highlighting. Future versions may allow editing and reload of JAPE files.

Author:
Mark A. Greenwood
